@snnn Thanks for your help, I followed the readme file and made some progress, but I got new problem like following:

"fatal: unable to access 'https://boringssl.googlesource.com/boringssl/': Fail
ed to connect to boringssl.googlesource.com port 443: Timed out
fatal: clone of 'https://boringssl.googlesource.com/boringssl' into submodule
path 'D:/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/cmake/build/grpc/src/grpc/third_party
/boringssl-with-bazel' failed"

I checked the google and fond the same Issue #6 in tensorflow/serving, but it looks not work for the last tensorflow, do you have idea how to solve this problem?
